data.description: This beautiful home listing features a 3-bedroom, 2-full bath brick ranch with a finished basement. It also boasts a new roof and a newer heat pump, ensuring a comfortable living environment. In addition to the mentioned features, the finished basement of this home includes a spacious den and a bedroom, providing ample space for various activities. The basement also features an updated bathroom and plenty of storage space, allowing for organized living. Outside, there are outbuildings available to accommodate any equipment needs.The property is situated in a peaceful setting and benefits from public water access and private septic. Sewer hookup will be available in the future. Additionally, its proximity to Kingsport, Johnson City, Bristol, and major highways offers convenient transportation options. Call for your showing today!!
